longBusinessSummary: Max Sound Corporation focuses on developing and launching audio technology software. The company was formerly known as So Act Network, Inc. and changed its name to Max Sound Corporation in March 2011. Max Sound Corporation was incorporated in 2005 and is based in San Diego, California.
